---
title: Sweet-Soy Beef & Noodles with Roasted Nuts
description: Sometimes you can’t go past the classics, like this beef stir-fry with a sweet and savoury sauce. With flat noodles and colourful
veggies, it tastes like a takeaway delight, but with the satisfaction of making it yourself!
